Bang Gwang-Suk binge reads a long but slowly serialized novel, [The Great Human-Demon War], over and over again, infatuated by the majestic world building and story development.
One day, he receives a mysterious message.
[This story ends here. Please use your power to save my world from ruin.]
Before he can get an answer to the questions in his mind, a new world was presented before his very eyesfrom the perspective of the Mad Emperor Exceltrion who would lead the world to ruins.
"That's right. I've become the mad emperor from the novel!"
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)

Mister Perfect A living legend in the realm of mixed martial arts, the Champion, Kim Sanghyuk, was somehow reborn in the Murim world as the youngest son of Keum Hojang! This time, Ill forge a new legend in the Murim! Against the backdrop of martial artists and untrained fighters scattered around Murim comes an oddity trained in Boxing, Taekwondo, Muay Thai, Wrestling, Jujitsu, Capoeira, Judo, and a variety of modern martial arts, ready to shake up the Murim!
